name: Sherrill, Mikie
message: Her judicial opinions on voting rights, gender discrimination, and same-sex marriage made this country stronger & will continue to ring out through the ages. She is a shining example of how one person can impact our world and truly make a difference. May her memory be a blessing.

name: Sherrill, Mikie
message:
Generations of women — my mother, myself, my sisters, my daughters — are indebted to her tenacity.

Decision by decision, Justice Ginsburg reaffirmed the ideals of our Constitution and our shared values of fairness, equality, and opportunity.

name: Sherrill, Mikie
message: We mourn the loss of an American icon. Justice Ginsburg was a pioneer and a role model for women across America. She's the reason women like me not only believed we had a right to be in the workplace, but were guaranteed it. She won us equality, and then showed us how to succeed. https://t.co/UDXlc8g4o7
